title: BBC Proms 2011_13 Verdi's Requiem
description:
Note: This torrent contains both a DVD ISO and an MP4 Video of the concert so I suggest you select whichever you prefer.

BBC Proms 2011, Number 13

Broadcast BBC4 on 21 August
Thanks to GringoLoco & the BBC

Verdi:
Requiem (86 mins)

Ferruccio Furlanetto: bass

BBC Symphony Chorus

London Philharmonic Choir

BBC Symphony Orchestra
Semyon Bychkov: conductor

Commentary in English
Fixed English subtitles
